OL,5, A former sub-postmistress has described
OL,6, how her life has been wrecked by the   
OL,7, Horizon Post Office software scandal.  
OL,9,FTracy McFadden ran a shop and post     
OL,10,Foffice in Sandiacre, Derbyshire, for   
OL,11,Fmore than 14 years until she was       
OL,12,Fwrongly accused of stealing #16,000.   
OL,14,FShe said the accusation had ruined her 
OL,15,Fsuccessful business, cost her her good 
OL,16,Fname, and left her "begging for        
OL,17,Fbenefits".                             
OL,19,FThe Post Office said it was aware of   
OL,20,Fthe "human cost of the scandal".       
